data.description: This Is It! A fantastic opportunity awaits for you to own an astounding 5 bedroom, 3 bath home with a 3-car garage and a fully fenced-in back yard in one of North Naples' greatest neighborhoods at an unbeatable price! This popular two-story "Flamingo" floor plan, with over 2900 square feet under air, has plenty of space to accommodate the whole family! You will LOVE the size of the expansive Master Bedroom with an extra seating area/ office space attached and the large on-suite bathroom with a jacuzzi tub. This home has been freshly painted inside & out, and features an updated kitchen, stainless steel appliances, crown molding, elegant baseboards, tile on the diagonal downstairs, new carpet, and more... Ready for a new owner! Saturnia Lakes is an active community offering many amenities and an excellent location. Amenities include- a wonderful Clubhouse, several pools, hot tub, fitness room, Internet cafe, 4 clay tennis courts, dance studio, saunas, massage rooms, billiards room, playground, basketball, miles of walking paths & more!
